1105
01:41:34,000 --> 01:41:35,700
Hajde, tri! Da, tri.

1106
01:41:38,900 --> 01:41:40,800
Bar se trudi, zar ne.

1107
01:41:41,000 --> 01:41:43,000
Ne brini. Dau ti melem za greve!

1108
01:41:42,900 --> 01:41:44,600
